title: United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Articles of Base Metal
description: Imports of Miscellaneous Articles of Base Metal in the United Kingdom increased to 204.28 GBP Million in September from 190.30 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Miscellaneous Articles of Base Metal in the United Kingdom averaged 127.79 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 252.41 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 63.45 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Articles of Base Metal.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
